window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Best-selling author Michael J. Sullivan’s mesmerizing Riyria Revelations series has found a welcome home with fans of magic, clashing swords, and daring heroes. This second volume finds Royce and Hadrian on a quest to enlist the southern Nationalists to aid the ever-weakening kingdom of Melengar. Royce suspects an ancient wizard is manipulating them all, but to find the truth he’ll have to decipher Hadrian’s past—a past Hadrian wants to keep secret.</p> <p><i>Rise of Empire</i> contains <i>Nyphron Rising</i> and <i>The Emerald Storm</i>, books 3 and 4 of Riyria Revelations.</p>"; 
